"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/765872","Ministry of Justice","false","2017-10-16","<p>The information requested is available at the following link:</p><p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/statistics/prisoner-transgender-statistics-march-to-april-2016" target="_blank">https://www.gov.uk/government/statistics/prisoner-transgender-statistics-march-to-april-2016</a>. Updated figures will be published next month.</p>","Bracknell","Dr Phillip Lee",,"2017-10-16T16:49:22.087Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/765872/answer","Biography information for Dr Phillip Lee","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/765872/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/765872/answer",,,,,"54","Justice","Justice","2017-10-06","Prisoners: Gender Recognition","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Justice, what recent estimate he has made of how many serving prisoners are transgender.","false","Biography information for David T. C. Davies","Monmouth","David T. C. Davies","106000"
